  "text": "Woohoo!! We are one month out from Easy Everyday! Today is the best day ever! Today, I’m launching the FREE bonus cookbook for Easy Everyday. This free bonus is available to you once you’ve preordered my next book, Easy Everyday which will be out on April 15! This bonus cookbook is called MAKE IT IN A FLASH! It includes 15 brand new recipes that take 20 minutes each. Yes! 15 new 20-minute recipes that are SO DELISH. Think pan crisp tacos, caprese farro salad, creamy cacio e pepe gnocchi, honey garlic smoked sausage and more. SO many more. All you have to do is preorder a copy of Easy Dinners and fill out this form to get your free bonus recipes. You will be sent an email with a link to download the bonus recipes! Easy Everyday will be your new everyday recipe bible!!!  It is packed with over 100 fantastic recipes, from breakfast to dinner to snacks to treats to mocktails and more. We have simple and flavorful dishes for every time time of day, some entertaining snacks, another one (!) of my signature sauces \u0026 dressings chapters (the fridge essentials that elevate everything!), so many tips for how I get meals prepped and ready for the week along with a lot of our family favorites. Along with so much more. You can preorder a SIGNED COPY HERE from Penguin Bookshop!!! There are a limited number of signed copies, so if you’d like a signed book, grab one HERE! Amazon Barnes \u0026 Noble Bookshop.org Books A Million Target Hudson Booksellers Apple Ebook Google Play Ebook  If you’ve already preordered prior to today, just enter your info here. It would mean everything to me if you preordered a copy. Preorders are the MOST important part of the book process. If you preorder, it will allow me to be able to write future books. It will let your favorite indie book stores know that Easy Everyday should be sold in stores. And it will allow me to do certain events for the book once it is released in April! I cannot thank you enough, because I only get to do this because of YOU. Now run and get your free bonus book, so you can tell me which if your favorite new recipe!",
