 creamy cacio e pepe gnocchi, honey garlic smoked sausage and more. SO many more.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/easy-everyday-bonus-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1698\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/03/get-your-free-easy-everyday-bonus-cookbook/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Get Your FREE(!!) Easy Everyday BONUS COOKBOOK!!\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/easy-everyday-bonus-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/easy-everyday-bonus-scaled.jpg 1698w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/easy-everyday-bonus-728x943.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/easy-everyday-bonus-768x995.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/easy-everyday-bonus-1185x1536.jpg 1185w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/easy-everyday-bonus-1580x2048.jpg 1580w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/easy-everyday-bonus-150x194.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1698px) 100vw, 1698px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201698%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/easy-everyday-bonus-scaled.jpg 1698w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/easy-everyday-bonus-728x943.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/easy-everyday-bonus-768x995.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/easy-everyday-bonus-1185x1536.jpg 1185w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/easy-everyday-bonus-1580x2048.jpg 1580w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/easy-everyday-bonus-150x194.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.hows